<p><img src="/images/Folder structure for google add setup.JPG" alt=""></p>
<p>Now, navigate to layout.ejs and place the below at location where you want to display the add</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;%- partial(&apos;googleadds/headeradd&apos;) %&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
